text:
sunny today's weather is sunny with
occasional clouds shining and warming

warming and shining rain the rain is
falling on the street
the snow is falling in the woods

drifting and floating floating and
drifting cold the cold man is struggling

to stay warm rubbing and blowing moving
and blowing hot the Sun is heating the
hitting and baking baking and heating

today's weather is sunny with occasional
clouds the rain is falling on the street
the snow is falling in the woods
the cold man is struggling to stay warm
the Sun is heating the hot desert
